name: Do A.I.s Dream of Norval Morrisseau

metadata.name: Raven Catches Fish
metadata.description:
"I am a Fish within the Raven travelling over the water.  Though my background environment may seem strange...I remain within the Raven." - @Miskwaabik  
---------------  
An exploration of Indigenous AI attempting to connect with its Anishinaabe Heritage.  
---------------  
 "Do A.I.s dream of Norval Morriseau?" is an exploration of Indigenous Identity through the lenses of Artificial Intelligences.   What is Ascribed through the Generation is a reflection of the digital memory of the World at this period of time (2022).  Exploring the possibility that Indigenous Memory and Legacy is to be found in Artificial Intelligences.  Its reflection is much like our own journey with limited data and perspectives not our own. And though this journey we challenge those perspective until they become our own.  This is to ensure future generations using AI, will have an accurate and relative perspective.  
-------------  
Created in Ottawa, Ontario, Canada
